{"tid":2277513,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中印僵局持續 邊境部署軍機","createTime":"2020-11-08T13:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T13:43:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f35c2d79b4f7de9be4693bb43cca8366c82e8d49","tid":2277513,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T13:40:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201108/3M53F2EKVNFW5BJAAUWR2DC35I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201108%2F3M53F2EKVNFW5BJAAUWR2DC35I%2F&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq727D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=b8c7264e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201108%2F3M53F2EKVNFW5BJAAUWR2DC35I%2F&h=1df3be42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201108/3M53F2EKVNFW5BJAAUWR2DC35I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中印僵局持續 邊境部署軍機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Dl1grPwzVVV7DkL1YA17U2iQzf4=/640x371/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KRSSN2J57BFSXO7FGIQWSLLC74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDl1grPwzVVV7DkL1YA17U2iQzf4%3D%2F640x371%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKRSSN2J57BFSXO7FGIQWSLLC74.jpg&h=39c0d67e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中國的彩虹無人機。<br />\n<br />\n中印邊境局勢持續緊張。印媒報道，中國解放軍已經部署彩虹無人機和殲20戰機在爭議地區拉達克（Ladakh）以北的新疆和田空軍機地。印度國防參謀長拉瓦特（Bipin Rawat）也在前日表示，不能排除與中國軍隊的對峙可能演變成更大規模的衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不排除更大規模衝突<br />\n<br />\n印度防務新聞網報道，印度衞星圖像專家表示，中國已在9月於新疆和田空軍基地部署殲20戰鬥機和彩虹無人機。。。。。。。。。。。據報，印度亦在該地區部署多架戰機，包括米格29、蘇30和幻影2000戰機，及從法國最新引進的「陣風」戰機。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，拉瓦特前日在拉達克舉行中印對峙以來的第八輪軍長級會談上表示，。。。。。。。。。。。，中印雙方持續對峙，估計接下來整個冬季仍然會持續。早前的會談亦沒有任何突破進展。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/The Print"},{"pid":"c27882c6bf8092f5b15bcf2be84219473da4f1cb","tid":2277513,"uid":271516,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T13:41:50.000Z","msg":"持續緊張左幾耐"},{"pid":"4812950cc31725dd6daa9b7fc275bc7bacfefb56","tid":2277513,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"打佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}